HEADWORD: Detort
<hw>De*tort"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p.
p.</pos> <conjf>Detorted</conjf>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Detorting</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L. <ets>detortus</ets>, p. p.
of <ets>detorquere</ets> to turn away; <ets>de</ets> +
