<ets>d⟦eacute⟧torquer</ets>, <ets>d⟦eacute⟧tordre</ets>.]</ety> <def>To
turn form the original or plain meaning; to pervert; to wrest.</def>
<rj><au>Hammond.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
